description: Rare opportunity! Unit 815 is one of the largest 1 bedrooms at Echelon. Located in the fabulous and vibrant Seaport District. This spacious and expansive 1 bed/1 bath offers extra sunlight and views of the city, courtyard and pool. Displaying floor-to-ceiling windows, an open floor-plan, modern kitchen with custom Italian flat panel cabinetry, one of the largest islands w/ Caesarstone quartz countertops, Thermador integrated appliances, many California Closets, and white oak plank floors throughout. Enhanced by a detailed marble-appointed bathroom with custom vanity and double sinks. Enjoy the 5-star services that this full service building offers and amenities like no other building in the city- 50,000 sq/ft of common space! Have the opportunity to use the private dining room, owners lounge, roof terrace, 3 pools (1 indoor, 2 outdoor), outdoor grills and fire pits, fitness center, spa, indoor basketball court, golf simulator, and much more!! Including 1 Valet Parking Space.
